<%- include ("../partials/header") %>
<div style="border: 4px solid #E3BE29" class="mainSegment p-5 container">
	<h1 style="text-align: center;" class="segmentHeading">Welcome to <span class="emph">AurParho</span></h1>
</div>
<div style="border: 4px solid #ed3e32" class="container mainSegment p-5 pt-0" >
	<div class="row" >
		<div class="col-12 d-flex d-md-none p-0 mb-4 d-flex justify-content-center" >
			<img src="https://i.ibb.co/JkSY89v/Artboard-4.png" class="jumboPic" calt="">
		</div>
		<div class="col-12 col-md-7 p-0" >
			<div class="col-12" >
				<h1 class="segmentHeading" >Introducing <span class="video" >Video Explanations</span></h1>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-8-sm col-12" >
				<p class="segmentPara" >Because sometimes, even pretty notes aren't enough. These videos, oriented specifically to people utilizing the notes on this website, will provide a <span class="video"> more engaging and comprehensive experience. </span></p>
				<p class="segmentPara" >Notes with video explanations have <span class="video"> red borders</span>, and the video link can be found below the download link. Alternatively, you could browse our <span class="video"> YouTube channel.</span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-5 p-0 m-0 d-none d-md-flex justify-content-end" >
			<img src="https://i.ibb.co/JkSY89v/Artboard-4.png" class="jumboPic marginManagement my-5" calt="">
		</div>
		<div class="col-8-sm col-12 jumboButton" style="margin-top: -30px;" >
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMNt3OYNFe-bYcCT_a1g86w" style="background-color: #ed3e32;" class="jumboLink p-3 px-4" >BROWSE CHANNEL</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>





<div class="container mainSegment p-5">
	<h1 class="segmentHeading">What's new in <span class="emph">v1.2</span>:</h1>
	<ul class="segmentPara">
		<li>Introduced video explanations for particular notes and many more coming soon</li>
		<li><span class="emph">[v1.2.1] </span> Videos are now embedded into each note's individual page instead of being YouTube links</li>
		<li>Added ability to click on note thumbnail instead of having to click on only the name</li>
		<li>Removed jumbotron slider, in favor of a static "Welcome to AurParho" message</li>
		<li>Notes on browse page are now sorted from most recent to oldest uploads</li>
	</ul>
</div>

